2003-05-28  Wez Furlong  <wez.php@thebrainroom.net>

    * (PHP_4_3)
      main/streams.c:
      On win32, always open in binary mode unless they asked for text mode using
      't'.
      This solves a number of apparent BC breaks that resulted from the move
      from
      fopen() to open().

