    * ext/rpc/com/com.c
      ext/rpc/com/com_wrapper.c
      ext/rpc/com/variant.h:
      Fix various little leaks and segfaults.
      Fix scripts like this:
      $obj = new COM('Foo');
      $obj2 = $obj->get_object();
      $obj2->method();  // <-- would segfault here

